   "body": "Wait until an enemy is mid-swing, then dodge at the last possible moment with X plus the stick: against a horizontal/sweeping side-slash, backflip (stick pulled back); against a vertical/overhead chop or a straight thrust, hop to the side (stick pushed left or right). A perfect dodge triggers slow-motion, and mashing Y then lands a flurry of free hits. This is the single most important combat skill, so practice it on weak enemies first."
