     "oneLine": "The half-built stable at Lookout Landing is missing a roof plank you can put in place.",
     "how": "Available after you clear one Regional Phenomena (one temple). Grab the loose wooden plank lying near the horses with Ultrahand, rotate it to fit the gap in the stable roof and set it in place to seal the hole, then talk to Karson/Lester to finish."
