     "oneLine": "Lester wants you to catch a particular spotted horse roaming the fields nearby.",
     "how": "Complete The Incomplete Stable first. Go a short way southwest to the wild horses near Passeri Greenbelt and find Spot — a beige horse with grey spots and a black mane and tail. Sneak up behind it, mount it, soothe it with the L-stick to tame it, then ride it back and register it with Lester while mounted."
